casebody.data:
DYNAMIC TRANSIT COMPANY, et al., petitioners,
v.
TRANS PACIFIC VENTURES, INC., et al. No. 13-260. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 2, 2013. Case below, 291 P.3d 114 .

Motion of Trucking Industry Defense Association for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Nevada denied.
